#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.vstack.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.vstack"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:1 of
msgid "Stack tensors in sequence vertically (row wise)."
msgstr "沿垂直方向（行方向）顺序堆叠张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:3 of
msgid ""
"This is equivalent to concatenation along the first axis after 1-D "
"tensors of shape `(N,)` have been reshaped to `(1,N)`. Rebuilds tensors "
"divided by `vsplit`."
msgstr ""
"这相当于在形状为 `(N,)` 的一维张量被重塑为 `(1,N)` 后，沿第一个轴进行连接"
"操作。该函数可以重建由 `vsplit` 分割的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:7 of
msgid ""
"This function makes most sense for tensors with up to 3 dimensions. For "
"instance, for pixel-data with a height (first axis), width (second axis),"
" and r/g/b channels (third axis). The functions `concatenate`, `stack` "
"and `block` provide more general stacking and concatenation operations."
msgstr ""
"此函数对于最多三维的张量最有意义。例如，对于具有高度（第一轴）、宽度（"
"第二轴）和 r/g/b 通道（第三轴）的像素数据。函数 `concatenate`、`stack` 和"
" `block` 提供了更通用的堆叠和连接操作。"

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:12 of
msgid ""
"The tensors must have the same shape along all but the first axis. 1-D "
"tensors must have the same length."
msgstr ""
"除了第一个轴之外，张量必须在所有其他轴上具有相同的形状。一维张量必须具有"
"相同的长度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:16 of
msgid ""
"**stacked** -- The tensor formed by stacking the given tensors, will be "
"at least 2-D."
msgstr "**stacked** -- 通过堆叠给定张量形成的张量，至少为二维。"

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:21 of
msgid ":py:obj:`stack`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:22 of
msgid "Join a sequence of tensors along a new axis."
msgstr "沿新轴连接一系列张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`concatenate`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:25 of
msgid "Join a sequence of tensors along an existing axis."
msgstr "沿现有轴连接一系列张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.merge.vstack.vstack:28 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

